file.content:
ï»¿# https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/master/versions/3.0.0.md#schemaObject
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple Document
  version: 0.9.1
paths: { }
components:
  schemas:
    ErrorModel:
      type: object
      required:
      - message
      - code
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
        code:
          type: integer
          minimum: 100
          maximum: 600
    ExtendedErrorModel:
      allOf:
      - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorModel'
      - type: object
        required:
        - rootCause
        properties:
          rootCause:
            type: string
